HEADWORD: Forpine
<hw>For*pine"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To waste away
completely by suffering or torment.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Pale as a <xex>forpined</xex> ghost.⟦rdquo⟧
